en:<p class=f>This book, like all books, was a labor of love. Oh sure, I got paid the medium-sized bucks for it, but nobody writes technical books for the money. And since this book is available on the web as well as on paper, I spent a lot of time fiddling with webby stuff when I should have been writing.
