en:<li>HTML is minimized, then served <a href=http://httpd.apache.org/docs/trunk/mod/mod_deflate.html>compressed</a>.
ja:<li>HTML is minimized, then served <a href=http://httpd.apache.org/docs/trunk/mod/mod_deflate.html>compressed</a>.

en:<li>Scripts and stylesheets are minimized by <a href=http://developer.yahoo.com/yui/compressor/>YUI Compressor</a> (and also served compressed).
ja:<li>Scripts and stylesheets are minimized by <a href=http://developer.yahoo.com/yui/compressor/>YUI Compressor</a> (and also served compressed).


en:<li>Scripts are combined to reduce HTTP requests.
ja:<li>Scripts are combined to reduce HTTP requests.


en:<li>Stylesheets are combined and inlined to reduce HTTP requests.
ja:<li>Stylesheets are combined and inlined to reduce HTTP requests.


en:<li>Unused CSS selectors and properties are <a href=http://hg.diveintopython3.org/file/default/util/lesscss.py>removed on a page-by-page basis</a> with a little help from <a href=http://pyquery.org/>pyquery</a>.
ja:<li>Unused CSS selectors and properties are <a href=http://hg.diveintopython3.org/file/default/util/lesscss.py>removed on a page-by-page basis</a> with a little help from <a href=http://pyquery.org/>pyquery</a>.


en:<li>HTTP caching and other server-side options are optimized based on advice from <a href=http://developer.yahoo.com/yslow/>YSlow</a> and <a href=http://code.google.com/speed/page-speed/>Page Speed</a>.
ja:<li>HTTP caching and other server-side options are optimized based on advice from <a href=http://developer.yahoo.com/yslow/>YSlow</a> and <a href=http://code.google.com/speed/page-speed/>Page Speed</a>.


en:<li>Pages use <a href=http://www.alanwood.net/unicode/unicode_samples.html>Unicode characters</a> in place of images wherever possible.
ja:<li>Pages use <a href=http://www.alanwood.net/unicode/unicode_samples.html>Unicode characters</a> in place of images wherever possible.


en:<li>Images are optimized with <a href=http://optipng.sourceforge.net/>OptiPNG</a>.
ja:<li>Images are optimized with <a href=http://optipng.sourceforge.net/>OptiPNG</a>.


